---
// Contact.astro
---

<section
  id="contact"
  class="relative bg-[#111113] px-6 py-32 border-t border-[#1C1C21]"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold text-[#F5F5F7] md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Conectemos
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-[#A1A1AA] text-lg">
        ¿Tienes un proyecto en mente o quieres conversar? Estaré encantado de escucharte.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-[#F5F5F7]">
            Información de Contacto
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[#A1A1AA] leading-relaxed">
            Estoy abierto a nuevas oportunidades, colaboraciones o proyectos
            interesantes donde pueda aportar valor como Desarrollador de Software.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a 
          href="mailto:samuel.sotomayor.t@gmail.com"
          class="inline-block group"
        >
          <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-[#C6A75E] transition-all group-hover:text-[#F5F5F7]">
            samuel.sotomayor.t@gmail.com
            <span class="block h-0.5 w-0 bg-[#C6A75E] transition-all group-hover:w-full"></span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <div class="pt-8">
          <h4 class="mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#A1A1AA]">
            Redes Sociales
          </h4>
          
          <div class="flex gap-5">
            <a href="https://github.com/SamuelSotomayor1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-[#1C1C21] bg-[#111113] text-[#A1A1AA] transition-all hover:border-[#C6A75E] hover:text-[#C6A75E] hover:-translate-y-1" aria-label="GitHub">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.28 1.15-.28 2.35 0 3.5-.73 1.02-1.08 2.25-1 3.5 0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"></path><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"></path></svg>
            </a>

            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/samuel-sotomayor-torrez-808800293/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-[#1C1C21] bg-[#111113] text-[#A1A1AA] transition-all hover:border-[#C6A75E] hover:text-[#C6A75E] hover:-translate-y-1" aria-label="LinkedIn">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"></rect><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle></svg>
            </a>

            <a href="https://twitter.com/Goal11_YT" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-[#1C1C21] bg-[#111113] text-[#A1A1AA] transition-all hover:border-[#C6A75E] hover:text-[#C6A75E] hover:-translate-y-1" aria-label="Twitter">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-[#1C1C21] bg-[#111113] p-10 text-center space-y-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#F5F5F7]">¿Listo para empezar?</h3>
        <p class="text-[#A1A1AA]">
          Descarga mi CV para conocer más detalles sobre mi formación y trayectoria técnica.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-4">
          <a 
            href="/Samuel_Sotomayor_CV.pdf" 
            download="Samuel_Sotomayor_CV.pdf"
            class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-[#C6A75E] px-8 py-4 font-bold text-black transition-all hover:bg-[#E6C77A] active:scale-95"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line></svg>
            DESCARGAR CV
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>